# Optional. With a Cesium ion token the app uses Cesium World Terrain (and you can later swap in
# Google Photorealistic 3D Tiles). WITHOUT a token it falls back to OpenStreetMap imagery on a flat
# ellipsoid — still renders the real I-595 location, just not 3D terrain. Get a token at
# https://ion.cesium.com/tokens   then:  cp .env.example .env  and fill this in.
VITE_CESIUM_ION_TOKEN=
